00:23:01,497 --> 00:23:03,230
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Motto hidup : Die hard! Never die!)</i></font>

368
00:23:03,232 --> 00:23:06,160
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku... hanya ingin hidup dalam waktu lama.</i></font>

