<font color=#FFFF00><i>dan menunjukkan foto kakaknya.</i></font>

433
00:26:27,970 --> 00:26:29,504
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Lalu, apakah Wang Young Choon...</i></font>

434
00:26:30,505 --> 00:26:32,741
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...membunuh kakaknya Wang Young Choon?</i></font>

435
00:26:36,378 --> 00:26:37,913
<font color=#FFFF00>- Oh?
- Sudah ketemu?</font>

436
00:26:38,647 --> 00:26:42,117
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah selesai menginvestigasi anggota Geng Tarantula.</font>

437
00:26:42,117 --> 00:26:45,187
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka sudah putus komunikasi dengan Wang Young Choon
