438
00:26:45,187 --> 00:26:46,421
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitukah?</font>

439
00:26:48,457 --> 00:26:49,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengerti.</font>

440
00:27:00,869 --> 00:27:04,506
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Moo Gang sebelum kehilangan ingatannya,
