497
00:30:10,392 --> 00:30:11,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya tidak ingat.</font>

498
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:13,461
<font color=#FFFF00>ANda tidak bisa mengingatnya?</font>

499
00:30:13,728 --> 00:30:14,963
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

500
00:30:15,463 --> 00:30:17,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Biasanya, dalam setahun... tidak.</font>

501
00:30:17,699 --> 00:30:20,669
